Using `simplexml_load_string()` with default settings is extremely dangerous and can lead to XXE (XML External Entity) attacks, including SSRF (Server-Side Request Forgery). Attackers can use malicious XML to make your server fetch internal resources, cloud metadata, or probe your internal network.

